# MeshFlow environment examples
#
# MeshFlow keeps runtime environment files app-local so frontend secrets never
# mix with backend credentials.
#
# Backend:
#   Copy backend/.env.example to backend/.env
#
# Frontend:
#   Copy frontend/.env.example to frontend/.env
#
# Do not commit .env files or real credentials.
# This root file is only a setup pointer; it is not loaded by the app.
